{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"body":"RESOLVED (joe-debug Step 6 replication PASS). After the fix auto-deployed, the rebar review bot cast LLM-Review+1 on open change 265 within ~80s; bot logs show the .tickets-tracker error GONE (remaining 409s are just stale backlog changes closed during the outage). Original report — 'bot casts no LLM-Review, fails with missing .tickets-tracker' — no longer reproduces. Two-vote gate fully restored for all agents."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1783140139370126001,"uuid":"2a555937-ebf6-475d-b08c-ecf360547e15"}